In [615]:
import itertools
p=d=q=range(0,3)
pdq=list(itertools.product(p,d,q))


ac=[]
dm=[]

for param in pdq:
    try:
        model_arima=ARIMA(train['Sales'], order=param)
        model_arima_fit=model_arima.fit()
        test['arima']= model_arima_fit.forecast(len(test))[0]
        ac.append(sqrt(mean_squared_error(test["Sales"], test['arima'])))
        dm.append(param)
    except:
        continue

param_select=pd.DataFrame()
param_select['param']=dm
param_select['rmsc']=ac
param_select.sort_values(['rmsc'], ascending=True, inplace=True)
param_select.head()

In [616]:
def adf_test(timeseries):
    print ('Results of Dickey-Fuller Test:')
    dftest = adfuller(timeseries, autolag='AIC')
    dfoutput = pd.Series(dftest[0:4], index=['Test Statistic','p-value','#Lags Used','Number of Observations Used'])
    for key,value in dftest[4].items():
        dfoutput['Critical Value (%s)'%key] = value
    print (dfoutput)
